Lt. Frank Drebbin returns to save the day once again. This time he's
out to foil the "big boys" in the energy business. A top scientist
(Dr Mainheimer) is about to publish his report on energy supply for
the future. Things don't look good for the traditional suppliers; oil,
coal and nuclear. To save their industries, the suppliers kidnap
Mainheimer and replace him with a decoy with a more favourable report
Jane, the Dr's secretary, is Drebbin's old flame; they're passionate
love affair is thus rekindled.
